[soft music]

41:24.883 --> 41:26.149
<i> Hola,</i> my son.

41:27.786 --> 41:29.786
What brings you in at this hour?

41:30.622 --> 41:32.589
Saw in a movie once that, um,

41:32.591 --> 41:34.824
devilish beings
can't go to church.

41:35.660 --> 41:37.026
It's a sanctuary.

41:38.964 --> 41:42.232
So I suppose I'm here
for that, a sanctuary.

41:42.834 --> 41:45.001
Santa Fe in English
means holy faith.

41:46.538 --> 41:49.038
So I think it's unlikely
you'll find any monsters

41:49.040 --> 41:50.607
in such a holy city.

41:52.511 --> 41:55.879
Tell me, are you a man
of faith, my son?

41:57.682 --> 41:59.015
I was raised in
a church, Father.

41:59.017 --> 42:01.985
But I haven't been
here in years.

42:01.987 --> 42:03.086
It's okay.

42:03.088 --> 42:04.621
You're here now.

42:05.891 --> 42:07.056
Oh, [chuckles],

42:07.792 --> 42:10.059
I'm Padre Esteban, by the way.

42:10.061 --> 42:11.794
Pat.

42:14.266 --> 42:15.965
You seem troubled, Pat.

42:16.968 --> 42:18.201
You want to talk about it?

42:19.204 --> 42:20.937
I'm a good listener.

42:20.939 --> 42:22.705
It's part of the job.

42:22.774 --> 42:25.542
-[light music]
-Well... [sighs]

42:27.646 --> 42:29.612
I've gotten myself into
a real pickle, Father.

42:30.649 --> 42:31.981
That's my fault.

42:33.318 --> 42:35.818
I did something
I knew it was wrong,

42:35.820 --> 42:37.186
but I agreed to do it anyway.

42:38.857 --> 42:39.989
And now I'm in trouble.

42:39.991 --> 42:41.758
Real trouble.

42:41.760 --> 42:43.126
Then why did you do it?

42:45.063 --> 42:46.129
Because...

42:47.332 --> 42:50.600
this man,
he was the closest thing

42:50.602 --> 42:52.735
I've ever known to a father.

42:52.804 --> 42:56.639
Actually cared about me,
for me, wanted the best for me.

42:58.143 --> 42:59.742
I thought he was a good guy.

43:03.615 --> 43:04.881
I just feel like a fool.

43:07.118 --> 43:12.221
People will disappoint,
but you must remember, Pat.

43:12.223 --> 43:14.724
Equally, people
will not disappoint.

43:15.627 --> 43:18.194
In fact, they will surprise
you with their kindness

43:18.196 --> 43:19.896
and the willingness to help you.

43:21.700 --> 43:24.634
And you, you shouldn't
feel like a fool.

43:26.338 --> 43:30.607
It sounds to me you did
this act, whatever it is,

43:30.609 --> 43:34.777
out of love and that
never makes you a fool.

43:34.779 --> 43:36.045
But I am a fool, Father.

43:36.114 --> 43:37.647
[chuckles]

43:37.649 --> 43:39.182
All you have to do for help...

43:40.952 --> 43:42.118
is ask.

43:44.089 --> 43:46.990
After all, this is
the city of holy faith.

43:47.993 --> 43:49.993
So have faith, Pat, hmm?

43:52.697 --> 43:53.896
What about you, Father?

43:56.067 --> 43:58.301
I mean, if you're
the one always doing

43:58.303 --> 44:00.937
all the listening,
who listens to you?

44:01.673 --> 44:04.073
[chuckles] No one's
ever asked me that.

44:05.076 --> 44:06.876
-[laughs]
-[sighs] Go on, Father.

44:07.812 --> 44:09.278
Try me, go on,
who listens to you?

44:10.148 --> 44:11.280
What's going on?

44:11.950 --> 44:12.982
Okay.

44:14.052 --> 44:16.119
Here goes young Pat, hmm.

44:17.822 --> 44:20.390
Our parishioners have not
been able to donate very much

44:20.392 --> 44:22.291
at all this year
for the toy drive.

44:23.328 --> 44:26.963
We try to put on a big
Christmas celebration

44:26.965 --> 44:28.965
for the less fortunate
children in town.

44:28.967 --> 44:30.933
[Patrick] Mm.

44:30.935 --> 44:33.803
[sighs] Especially those
who do not have families,

44:34.973 --> 44:40.143
but this year, hmm, I don't
know what we're going to do.

44:42.847 --> 44:44.914
-You seem troubled, Father?
-I am.

44:47.886 --> 44:50.186
They so look forward
to this all year.

44:51.022 --> 44:53.790
For some of them, it's all
they have to look forward to.

44:55.193 --> 44:56.426
And I confess... [chuckling]

44:58.129 --> 45:00.830
...it gives me joy to
do this for them.

45:01.866 --> 45:06.869
My heart aches for them all,
but when I see the happiness

45:06.871 --> 45:10.406
on their faces
then I know it helps.

45:12.210 --> 45:14.444
So, what will you do?

45:14.446 --> 45:17.780
Pray and I believe

45:18.750 --> 45:20.216
God will provide.

45:22.053 --> 45:25.855
After all, Father, it's a city
of holy faith now, isn't it?

45:26.858 --> 45:28.958
-[light music]
-[chuckles]

45:30.261 --> 45:32.061
Thank you, my son.

45:33.998 --> 45:36.933
[Jim] Now that's
what I call a church.

45:36.935 --> 45:38.468
Look at that. [chuckles]

