for new opportunity,

50:05.136 --> 50:07.603
and who was it that
said go west, young man?

50:07.605 --> 50:08.704
[laughing]

50:10.575 --> 50:13.009
[Spanish themed guitar music]

50:27.125 --> 50:28.257
Thank you.

50:36.434 --> 50:38.300
