your coat from the hostess?

51:31.589 --> 51:33.489
No, no, no.
No, it's fine, it's fine.

51:33.491 --> 51:35.691
Your body heat actually
leaves from your head,

51:35.693 --> 51:39.361
so it's amazing how comfortable
a hat can make you feel, yeah.

51:40.198 --> 51:42.131
Marvelous feat of
engineering really.

51:43.434 --> 51:45.568
Okay, whatever you say.

51:55.446 --> 51:57.346
