a friend out there about

53:19.664 --> 53:21.463
the lyrics to a Christmas carol.

53:21.866 --> 53:23.399
Help me out, will you?

53:23.401 --> 53:25.234
I came in here
to stall for time,

53:25.236 --> 53:27.403
