collect toys for charity.

01:14:55.592 --> 01:14:56.891
You know, just for Christmas.

01:14:56.893 --> 01:14:59.660
Didn't it look a little
old-fashioned to you?

01:14:59.662 --> 01:15:01.262
Of course, it looked
old-fashioned, Emily.

01:15:01.531 --> 01:15:04.131
Everything in Santa Fe
is old fashioned, all right?

01:15:04.133 --> 01:15:06.968
Calm down, Pat,
we can figure this out.

01:15:07.036 --> 01:15:09.237
What's to figure out, Emily?

01:15:12.108 --> 01:15:13.491
When I'll get deported?

01:15:13.492 --> 01:15:14.875
I mean, 'cause, you know what?
It's not if, it's when.

01:15:14.878 --> 01:15:16.711
Oh, actually, I know when.

01:15:16.713 --> 01:15:19.647
When I finish my jail sentence
in an American prison.

01:15:19.649 --> 01:15:20.848
And do you know what?

01:15:20.850 --> 01:15:22.984
Joe has like these
big long tentacles.

01:15:23.052 --> 01:15:25.152
And he's like octopus that like,
go through to the jail cell.

01:15:25.154 --> 01:15:26.854
He's like this big
Irish octopus.

01:15:26.856 --> 01:15:28.956
I don't know.
He told me so himself.

01:15:29.025 --> 01:15:30.591
-[thudding]
-Stupid door.

01:15:30.660 --> 01:15:32.193
-[Pat screaming]
-[Emily yelps]

01:15:38.001 --> 01:15:40.034
[reindeer slobbering]

01:15:46.876 --> 01:15:49.544
The top of my head all wet
and warm, I'm bleeding.

01:15:49.546 --> 01:15:52.613
-It's blood.
-[man] It's not blood.

01:15:52.615 --> 01:15:54.181
It's reindeer slobber.

01:15:55.151 --> 01:15:57.318
Dunder, stop eating his hair.

01:15:57.320 --> 01:15:58.753
It's not good for you.

01:15:59.722 --> 01:16:01.255
I'm sorry about this.

01:16:01.257 --> 01:16:03.858
Every now and again
he nips at my beard

01:16:03.860 --> 01:16:05.860
when he's real hungry.

01:16:05.929 --> 01:16:07.128
Dunder?

01:16:07.130 --> 01:16:09.897
[man] Well, for you
native English speakers.

01:16:09.899 --> 01:16:11.766
It's Donner.

01:16:11.768 --> 01:16:14.168
Dunder means thunder in Dutch.

01:16:14.170 --> 01:16:15.336
[reindeer belching]

01:16:15.338 --> 01:16:16.637
See what I mean?

01:16:16.639 --> 01:16:18.139
[Santa chuckles]

01:16:18.141 --> 01:16:19.140
[chimes]

01:16:19.208 --> 01:16:20.675
[light music]

01:16:26.816 --> 01:16:28.215
Sir, this is, uh,
this is great and all,

01:16:28.217 --> 01:16:29.951
but I have
the authorities chasing me.

01:16:29.953 --> 01:16:33.220
Please, it wouldn't be
Christmas if I didn't have

01:16:33.222 --> 01:16:35.356
a few run-ins with the police.

01:16:35.625 --> 01:16:38.793
