01:16:52.175 --> 01:16:54.742
Isn't it obvious,
I'm Santa Claus.

01:16:55.278 --> 01:16:57.244
You can call me Santa.

01:16:57.313 --> 01:16:59.246
-Santa?
-Santa Claus?

