the day you were born.

01:17:17.400 --> 01:17:23.137
One of my elves, Alowishus,
he alerted me to your unusual

01:17:23.139 --> 01:17:26.240
sense of caring,
your special gifts.

01:17:27.877 --> 01:17:30.745
Look, Pat, I want
to offer you a job.

01:17:31.214 --> 01:17:34.215
